  =item B<--filter-counters>
  
  Only display some counters (regexp can be used).
  Example to check SSL connections only : --filter-counters='^xxxx|yyyy$'
  
  =item B<--warning-*>
  
  Threshold warning.
  Can be: 'xxx', 'xxx'.
  
  =item B<--critical-*>
  
  Threshold critical.
  Can be: 'xxx', 'xxx'.
  
  =back
  
